one","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question-2":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What material are the caster wheels made of?","text":"<p>The wheels are made from TPR (thermoplastic rubber), which provides quiet rolling performance and helps protect indoor floors from marking.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question-3":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What does 3\/8\\\"-16 x 1-1\/2\\\" threaded stem mean?","text":"<p>It refers to the stem diameter, thread pitch, and stem length. These casters are designed to fit mounting sockets compatible with 3\/8\\\"-16 threaded stems with a 1-1\/2\\\" depth.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question-4":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What is the difference between side brake and no brake casters?","text":"<p>Side brake casters allow you to lock the wheel to prevent rolling, while no brake casters provide continuous free movement.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question-5":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are these caster wheels suitable for hardwood or tile floors?","text":"<p>Yes. The TPR wheels are non-marking and designed to roll smoothly on hardwood, tile, vinyl, and other indoor flooring surfaces.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_Ycgbaw":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are these stem casters sold individually or as a set?","text":"<p>These stem casters are typically sold as a set. Please refer to the product options for available pack sizes.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_c99pAa":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What if I choose the wrong option?","text":"<p>If you’re unsure which option fits your setup, feel free to contact us before ordering.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"contact":{"type":"contact","settings":{"heading":"Didn’t find your answer?","